{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01SDMxkJ7JdeRS4J7uthJkHe","type":"tool_result","content":"   692→### `cloche status`\n   693→\n   694→```\n   695→cloche status [<run-id>] [--all]\n   696→```\n   697→\n   698→With a run ID, shows run title, type (`host`/`container`), state, active steps, and\n   699→per-step results.\n   700→\n   701→Without a run ID, shows a daemon status overview: version, run statistics (past hour),\n   702→and active runs. In a project directory, also shows project name, concurrency, and\n   703→orchestration loop state. Use `--all` to show global stats instead of project-specific\n   704→stats.\n   705→\n   706→| Flag | Description |\n   707→|------|-------------|\n   708→| `--all` | Show global stats instead of project-specific stats. |\n   709→\n   710→### `cloche list`\n   711→\n   712→```\n   713→cloche list [flags]\n   714→```\n   715→\n   716→Lists runs for the current project directory. Pass `--all` to show runs across all projects.\n   717→Results can be filtered by state, project, issue, or limited to a fixed number.\n   718→\n   719→| Flag | Description |\n   720→|------|-------------|\n   721→| `--all` | Show runs from all projects (default: current project only). |"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"11647995-5bb5-4c45-b565-ed9e3d641bc0","uuid":"41a1b198-1e27-45e9-92ff-74997039d820","timestamp":"2026-03-17T15:56:03.189Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","content":"### `cloche status`\n\n```\ncloche status [<run-id>] [--all]\n```\n\nWith a run ID, shows run title, type (`host`/`container`), state, active steps, and\nper-step results.\n\nWithout a run ID, shows a daemon status overview: version, run statistics (past hour),\nand active runs. In a project directory, also shows project name, concurrency, and\norchestration loop state. Use `--all` to show global stats instead of project-specific\nstats.\n\n| Flag | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `--all` | Show global stats instead of project-specific stats. |\n\n### `cloche list`\n\n```\ncloche list [flags]\n```\n\nLists runs for the current project directory. Pass `--all` to show runs across all projects.\nResults can be filtered by state, project, issue, or limited to a fixed number.\n\n| Flag | Description |\n|------|-------------|\n| `--all` | Show runs from all projects (default: current project only). |","numLines":30,"startLine":692,"totalLines":994}}}
